---
// Marsal Business Launchpad — canonical URL: /services/marsal-business-launchpad/

import Layout from "../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
import ContactUs from "../../components/ContactUs.astro";

// Sidebar menu items - Marsal Business Launchpad is active
const sidebarItems = [
  { text: "Accounting Services", href: "/services/accounting/" },
  { text: "Bookkeeping Services", href: "/services/bookkeeping/" },
  { text: "Management Accounts Services", href: "/services/management-accounts/" },
  { text: "Payroll Services", href: "/services/payroll/" },
  { text: "Property Accounts Services", href: "/services/property-accounts/" },
  { text: "Self Assessment Tax Returns", href: "/services/self-assessment-tax-returns/" },
  { text: "Corporation Tax Return", href: "/services/corporation-tax-return-services/" },
  { text: "Marsal Business Launchpad", href: "/services/marsal-business-launchpad/", active: true },
  { text: "Tax Investigation", href: "/services/tax-investigation/" },
  { text: "Value Added Tax Services", href: "/services/vat/" },
];

// Carousel items (same as other pages)
const carouselItems = [
  { text: "<strong>QUALITY</strong> SERVICE DELIVERED ON TIME" },
  { text: "<strong>FREE PHONE</strong> HELP LINE ON DAY TO DAY ACCOUNTING, TAX, EMPLOYMENT ISSUES......." },
  { text: "WE COLLECT &amp; RETURN YOUR <strong>DOCUMENTS</strong>" },
  { text: "FIXED COMPETITIVE FEES FOR ALL <strong>SERVICES</strong>" },
  { text: "DEDICATED CONSULTANT WHO VISITS YOU REGULARLY MAKING SURE YOUR <strong>ACCOUNTING &amp; TAX AFFAIRS</strong> ARE UP TO DATE", class: "small" },
  { text: "WE ARE CARING <strong>ACCOUNTANTS</strong>..... WE PUT OURSELVES IN YOUR SHOES" },
  { text: "<strong>ACCOUNTANTS</strong> WHO SPEAK AND UNDERSTAND YOUR LANGUAGE" },
  { text: "WE VISIT YOU TO DISCUSS <strong>ACCOUNTS</strong>" },
];
---

<Layout title="Marsal Business Launchpad | Marsal Accountants Paisley">
  <main class="services-detail-page">
    
    <!-- Carousel Section -->
    <div class="carousel-section">
      <div id="carousel-text" class="carousel">
        <div class="carousel-inner">
          {carouselItems.map((item, index) => (
            <div 
              class={`item ${index === 0 ? 'active' : ''} ${item.class || ''}`}
              key={index}
              set:html={item.text}
            />
          ))}
        </div>
      </div>
      <hr class="carousel-divider">
    </div>

    <!-- Main Content Container -->
    <div class="service-detail-container">
      <div class="service-detail-grid">
        
        <!-- Main Content Column -->
        <div class="service-detail-main">
          <h2 class="service-detail-heading">Marsal Business Launchpad</h2>
          <div class="divider-content"></div>
          
          <div class="service-detail-content">
            <p>Marsal Business Launchpad gives founders a clear set of startup packages, from registration-only support to a full launch bundle that includes strategy, formation, registrations, website build, hosting, domain, and professional email.</p>
            <p>These are our published package prices and line items, designed to stay transparent before and after Marsal Business Launchpad - 40 Under 40 launches.</p>

            <h4 class="service-mini-heading">Published Line Item Pricing</h4>
            <div class="divider-content-small"></div>
            <ul class="content-bullet">
              <li>Initial Business Strategy Consultation – £200</li>
              <li>Company Incorporation – £100</li>
              <li>Formation Administration Support – £60</li>
              <li>Companies House Authentication Code Setup – £20</li>
              <li>Self-Employment Registration Administration – £40</li>
              <li>Payroll Scheme Registration – £100</li>
              <li>VAT Registration – £150</li>
              <li>12-Month Professional Web Hosting – £120</li>
              <li>12-Month Domain Name Registration – £20</li>
              <li>12-Month Professional Business Email Account – £20</li>
              <li>3-Page Professional Business Website – £700</li>
            </ul>

            <h4 class="service-mini-heading">Launchpad Packages</h4>
            <div class="divider-content-small"></div>
            <ul class="content-bullet">
              <li><strong>Package 1 - Core Registration (£180):</strong> Company Incorporation, Formation Administration Support, Companies House Authentication Code Setup.</li>
              <li><strong>Package 2 - Advice + Registration (£380):</strong> Initial Business Strategy Consultation plus Package 1.</li>
              <li><strong>Package 3 - Registration + Website (£1,040):</strong> Package 1 plus Website, Hosting, Domain, and 1 Professional Business Email.</li>
              <li><strong>Package 4 - Founder Launch (Advice + Reg + Website) (£1,240):</strong> Package 2 plus Website, Hosting, Domain, and 1 Professional Business Email.</li>
              <li><strong>Package 5 - Growth Compliance Add-On (+£250):</strong> Payroll Scheme Registration and VAT Registration.</li>
              <li><strong>Package 6 - Sole Trader Starter (£240):</strong> Initial Business Strategy Consultation and Self-Employment Registration Administration.</li>
              <li><strong>Package 7 - Founding Bundle (40 Under 40 Equivalent) (£1,530):</strong> Full formation support plus digital launch package.</li>
            </ul>

            <h4 class="service-mini-heading">40 Under 40 Alignment</h4>
            <div class="divider-content-small"></div>
            <p>The Marsal Business Launchpad - 40 Under 40 programme is not yet open. When launched, selected recipients receive the Founding Bundle (or equivalent) free of charge, subject to programme eligibility, draw rules, and terms.</p>

            <h4 class="service-mini-heading">Build Your Best-Fit Package</h4>
            <div class="divider-content-small"></div>
            <p>If you only need registration, we can deliver that. If you need strategy, digital launch, registrations, and compliance setup together, we can build a practical full-launch route around your goals.</p>
            <p><a href="/contact/">Contact us</a> today to choose your package and get started.</p>

            <div class="contact-info">
              <h4>Call us on <a href="tel:07468641272" class="contact-link">074-6864-1272</a> or email <a href="mailto:info@marsalaccountants.co.uk" class="contact-link">info@marsalaccountants.co.uk</a> to get started.</h4>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Sidebar Column -->
        <aside class="services-sidebar">
          <div class="sidebar-header">
            <h3>Services</h3>
          </div>
          <div class="sidebar-content">
            <ul id="submenu">
              {sidebarItems.map((item) => (
                <li class={item.active ? 'active' : ''}>
                  <a href={item.href}>{item.text}</a>
                </li>
              ))}
            </ul>
          </div>
        </aside>

      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Contact Us Component -->
    <ContactUs />

  </main>

  <style is:global>
    /* Service Detail Page Styles */
    .services-detail-page {
      padding-top: 40px;
      padding-bottom: 80px;
      background: var(--color-surface);
      min-height: calc(100vh - 300px);
    }

    /* Carousel Styles */
    .carousel-section {
      max-width: 1200px;
      margin: 0 auto 3rem;
      padding: 0 20px;
    }

    #carousel-text {
      text-align: center;
      margin-bottom: 2rem;
    }

    .carousel-inner {
      position: relative;
      height: 80px;
      overflow: hidden;
    }

    .carousel-inner .item {
      position: absolute;
      width: 100%;
      opacity: 0;
      transition: opacity 1s ease-in-out;
      font-size: 1.4rem;
      font-weight: 500;
      color: var(--color-text);
      line-height: 1.6;
      top: 0;
      left: 0;
    }

    .carousel-inner .item.active {
      opacity: 1;
    }

    .carousel-inner .item.small {
      font-size: 1.2rem;
    }

    .carousel-inner strong {
      color: var(--color-primary);
      font-weight: 700;
    }

    .carousel-divider {
      max-width: 800px;
      height: 1px;
      margin: 2.5rem auto;
      background: linear-gradient(90deg, 
          transparent 0%, 
          var(--color-border) 20%, 
          var(--color-border) 80%, 
          transparent 100%);
      border: none;
      opacity: 0.8;
    }

    /* Main Container */
    .service-detail-container {
      max-width: 1200px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 0 20px;
    }

    .service-detail-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 300px;
      gap: 3rem;
    }

    /* Main Content Styles */
    .service-detail-main {
      background: var(--color-surface-card);
      border-radius: 16px;
      padding: 2.5rem;
      box-shadow: var(--shadow-md);
      border: 1px solid var(--color-border-light);
    }

    .service-detail-heading {
      font-size: 2rem;
      font-weight: 800;
      color: var(--color-primary);
      margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    }

    .service-subheading {
      font-size: 1.5rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      color: var(--color-text);
      margin: 2rem 0 1rem;
    }

    .service-mini-heading {
      font-size: 1.3rem;
      font-weight: 600;
      color: var(--color-primary);
      margin: 2rem 0 0.5rem;
    }

    .service-detail-content p {
      font-size: 1.05rem;
      line-height: 1.7;
      color: var(--color-text-secondary);
      margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    }

    .service-detail-content a {
      color: var(--color-primary);
      text-decoration: none;
      font-weight: 600;
      transition: color var(--transition-fast);
    }

    .service-detail-content a:hover {
      color: var(--color-primary-dark);
      text-decoration: underline;
    }

    /* External link indicator */
    .service-detail-content a[target="_blank"]::after {
      content: "↗";
      font-size: 0.9em;
      margin-left: 2px;
      display: inline-block;
    }

    /* Divider Styles */
    .divider-content {
      width: 100%;
      height: 3px;
      background: linear-gradient(90deg, 
          var(--color-primary) 0%, 
          var(--color-primary-light) 50%, 
          var(--color-primary) 100%);
      margin: 1.5rem 0 2rem;
      border-radius: 2px;
    }

    .divider-content-small {
      width: 80px;
      height: 3px;
      background: var(--color-primary);
      border-radius: 2px;
      margin: 0.8rem 0 1.5rem;
    }

    /* Bulleted List */
    .content-bullet {
      list-style: none;
      padding-left: 1.5rem;
      margin: 1.5rem 0;
    }

    .content-bullet li {
      position: relative;
      padding-left: 1.5rem;
      margin-bottom: 0.8rem;
      font-size: 1.05rem;
      line-height: 1.6;
      color: var(--color-text-secondary);
    }

    .content-bullet li::before {
      content: "✓";
      position: absolute;
      left: 0;
      color: var(--color-primary);
      font-weight: bold;
    }

    /* Contact Info */
    .contact-info {
      background: var(--color-primary-light);
      border-radius: 12px;
      padding: 2rem;
      margin-top: 3rem;
      text-align: center;
    }

    .contact-info h4 {
      font-size: 1.3rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      color: var(--color-text);
      margin: 0;
      display: flex;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      justify-content: center;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 0.5rem;
    }

    .contact-link {
      color: var(--color-primary);
      text-decoration: none;
      font-weight: 600;
      transition: color var(--transition-fast);
    }

    .contact-link:hover {
      color: var(--color-primary-dark);
      text-decoration: underline;
    }

    /* Sidebar Styles */
    .services-sidebar {
      position: sticky;
      top: 100px;
      height: fit-content;
    }

    .sidebar-header {
      background: var(--color-primary);
      color: var(--color-text-on-primary);
      padding: 1rem 1.5rem;
      border-radius: 12px 12px 0 0;
      font-size: 1.3rem;
      font-weight: 700;
    }

    .sidebar-content {
      background: var(--color-surface-card);
      border-radius: 0 0 12px 12px;
      padding: 1.5rem;
      border: 1px solid var(--color-border-light);
      border-top: none;
    }

    #submenu {
      list-style: none;
      padding: 0;
      margin: 0;
    }

    #submenu li {
      margin-bottom: 0.8rem;
    }

    #submenu a {
      display: block;
      padding: 0.6rem 0.8rem;
      border-radius: 8px;
      color: var(--color-text-secondary);
      text-decoration: none;
      font-size: 0.95rem;
      font-weight: 500;
      transition: all var(--transition-fast);
    }

    #submenu a:hover {
      background: var(--color-primary-light);
      color: var(--color-text-on-primary);
      transform: translateX(4px);
    }

    #submenu .active a {
      background: var(--color-primary);
      color: var(--color-text-on-primary);
    }

    /* Responsive Design */
    @media (max-width: 1024px) {
      .service-detail-grid {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
        gap: 2rem;
      }

      .services-sidebar {
        position: relative;
        top: 0;
      }

      .carousel-inner .item {
        font-size: 1.2rem;
      }

      .carousel-inner .item.small {
        font-size: 1.1rem;
      }
    }

    @media (max-width: 768px) {
      .services-detail-page {
        padding-top: 20px;
        padding-bottom: 40px;
      }

      .service-detail-main {
        padding: 1.5rem;
      }

      .service-detail-heading {
        font-size: 1.8rem;
      }

      .service-subheading {
        font-size: 1.3rem;
      }

      .service-mini-heading {
        font-size: 1.2rem;
      }

      .carousel-inner {
        height: 100px;
      }

      .carousel-inner .item {
        font-size: 1.1rem;
      }

      .carousel-inner .item.small {
        font-size: 1rem;
      }

      .contact-info h4 {
        flex-direction: column;
        gap: 0.5rem;
      }
    }

    @media (max-width: 480px) {
      .carousel-inner {
        height: 120px;
      }

      .carousel-inner .item {
        font-size: 1rem;
      }

      .service-detail-heading {
        font-size: 1.6rem;
      }

      .service-subheading {
        font-size: 1.2rem;
      }

      .service-mini-heading {
        font-size: 1.1rem;
      }
    }

    /* Dark Mode */
    [data-theme="dark"] .service-detail-main {
      background: var(--color-surface-elevated);
      border-color: var(--color-border);
    }

    [data-theme="dark"] .sidebar-content {
      background: var(--color-surface-elevated);
      border-color: var(--color-border);
    }

    [data-theme="dark"] .contact-info {
      background: var(--color-primary-dark);
    }
  </style>

  <!-- Carousel JavaScript -->
  <script is:inline>
    document.addEventListener('DOMContentLoaded', () => {
      const carouselItems = document.querySelectorAll('.carousel-inner .item');
      let currentIndex = 0;
      const intervalTime = 6000; // 6 seconds

      function showNextItem() {
        // Hide current item
        carouselItems[currentIndex].classList.remove('active');
        
        // Move to next item
        currentIndex = (currentIndex + 1) % carouselItems.length;
        
        // Show next item
        carouselItems[currentIndex].classList.add('active');
      }

      // Initialize first item
      carouselItems[currentIndex].classList.add('active');

      // Start carousel
      let carouselInterval = setInterval(showNextItem, intervalTime);

      // Pause on hover
      const carousel = document.getElementById('carousel-text');
      if (carousel) {
        carousel.addEventListener('mouseenter', () => {
          clearInterval(carouselInterval);
        });

        carousel.addEventListener('mouseleave', () => {
          carouselInterval = setInterval(showNextItem, intervalTime);
        });
      }
    });
  </script>
</Layout>
